-- 
Faurecia to Expand Production in Slovakia, Hospodarske Reports

-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 
2011-07-21T07:02:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/faurecia-to-expand-production-in-slovakia-hospodarske-reports.html
Faurecia (EO)  SA plans to invest 11.5
million euros ($16.4 million) to expand production in Slovakia,
 Hospodarske Noviny  reported.  The French maker of car interiors and other auto parts will
create about 150 new jobs at its existing factory in Hlohovec,
western Slovakia, the newspaper said, citing an environment
ministry document.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net . 